lead_paragraph: The Dodgers mustered just one hit off Zack Greinke through three innings. Then their former teammate faltered and Los Angeles hammered the former Cy Young Award winner for five home runs.

headline.print_headline: Hammer Time: Dodgers Hit 5 HRs in 10-2 Win Over Arizona
